    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that looks and drives like new, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
