    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally bulletproofed. The power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry for precise turn-in. Finished in a rare paint-to-sample hue with a flawless interior, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience with zero mechanical compromises. A turn-key masterpiece for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
