    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its original factory luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is flawless, boasting a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships and incredibly low mileage. Every feature, from the advanced driver-assistance systems to the high-fidelity sound system, functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes two keys, all original manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 47900.0,
