      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to drive this beauty next. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in stunning, showroom-ready shape. It looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
