    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: the critical rod bearing service has been completed, the Vanos system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure long-term structural rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, providing linear power delivery and exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with refreshed bushings and a pristine underside. This is a collector-grade specimen with flawless paint depth and an interior that shows no signs of bolster wear or UV degradation, offering a pure, analog driving experience.",
